@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

@{MS "Introduction"}

MCControl is a tool for all PSX owners. It's a hard and software project to read and write your
memory cards.@{par}

So there is no need to buy new bigger memory cards. Just one card is needed to store all your save
games.@{par}

MCControl allows to import savegames from internet, so you'll get access to features and stages
you've never been before.@{par}

@endnode
@node "Systemrequirements" "Systemrequirements"

@{MS "System requirements"}

MCControl (should work) works on all Amigas with OS 2.0 or higher.@{par}

The @{b}gtdrag.library V3.2+@{ub} is required if you want to use the drag and drop features. I
suggest to use this library if possible, because the only other way to move save games between
windows is to save and reload. @{b}The gtdrag.library requires OS3.x+ and a 68020 or
better!@{ub}@{par}

A PSX and a MemoryCard should be around, too! (-8@{par}

You need a @{"DexDrive" link "FAQSDexDrive"}, a @{"PSXPort" link "FAQSPSXPort"} or you must build a
special @{"hardware" link "Hardware"}!@{par}


   That`s all!
@endnode
@node "Featurelist" "Features"

@{MS "Features"}

  ° 100% Assembler@{par}

  ° Load and save the following files: MCD, VGS, GME, PSM, PSX, MEM@{par}

  ° Displays PSX Images.@{par}

  ° Special hardware versions for @{"parallel" link "HardPara"} and @{"disk port" link "HardDisk"}.@{par}

  ° @{"DexDrive Support" link "FAQSDexDrive"}@{par}

  ° @{"DataDeck Support" link "FAQSDataDeck"}@{par}

  ° @{"PSXPort Support" link "FAQSPSXPort"}@{par}

  ° Very quick MemoryCard access! (Internal Caching)@{par}

  ° Open as much virtual MemoryCards as you need.@{par}

  ° Drag'n Drop allows to move save games very easy between virtual MemoryCards.@{par}

  ° A @{"save game converter" link "Patc"} allows to use any international save game!@{par}

  ° A @{"save game manipulator" link "Patc"} to reach stages you never saw before!@{par}

  ° XPK support@{par}

  ° Locale support@{par}

@endnode
@node "Distribution" "Distribution"

@{MS "Distribution"}

This program should be published on every public medium, as long as all files in the archive are
unchanged. If this medium is a CD I expect a free copy. (AminetCDs excluded)@{par}

@{b}Blittersoft is allowed to sell this archive within their @{"PSXPort" link "FAQSPSXPort"}
packet!@{ub}@{par}

@{b}MCControl is Mailware.@{ub}@{par}

I expect from everybody, who uses MCControl regularly, to send me an email or postcard. I think this
does not hurt anybody, and I will have more fun to integrate new features. In addition to that it's
possible to insert your EMail address into my MCControl mailing list. So you'll get access to pre
releases and additional information about MCControl.@{par}

@{b}I am not liable for injures or data loss caused by MCControl or the
@{"hardware" link "hardware"}. The use of MCControl is on your own responsibility !!!@{ub}

@endnode
@node "HowToInstall" "How to install MCControl"

@{MS "How to install MCControl"}

Please use the original @{b}system installer@{ub} for installation. This allows to create a memory
and hard disk optimized installation.@{par}

Well, its also possible to drag the MCControl drawer onto your hard disk, but - as I said above -
you are wasting hard disk and memory.@{par}

Thats all!@{par}

Don't forget to build the @{"CardReader" link "Hardware"}!! (-8

