auto play and the repeat mode. If MCControl is crashing or freezing, then its required to update
both files. On Aminet there is a animation.datatype replacement "animation4106.lha"! This datatype
is working much better, but a crash may appear, too! So don't blame me for such problems! Contact
the developer of the AmigaOS insteed!@{ub}


