   Save 1:1     - 16*16 pixel, Store the images like they are!@{par}
   Save 2:2     - 32*32 pixel, Double X and Y.@{par}
   Save 2:1     - 32*16 pixel, Double X only.@{par}
   No Icons     - Disables icon creation!@{par}

Note: The system default icons are named "def_PSXMemoryCard.info" and "def_PSXSaveGame.info"!


The icon mode only effects MemoryCard icons when icon creation is disabled. Any other setup will
cause the usage of the default icon. If no default PSXMemoryCard icon is available the default
project icon will be used.

